	h3
		b Basis of metric (to Riemann)
	p The metric depends on the basis too:
	p \(g_{ij}(p)=g((\dfrac{\delta }{\delta x^i})_p,(\dfrac{\delta }{\delta x^j})_p)\)

	p The metric on two tangent vectors is defined on the components.
	p \(g=g_{ij}(p)u^iv^j\)

